Description:
    This generator provides a scaffold for Ekylibre

Example:
    rails generate backend_scaffold MyModel

    This will create: 
        route
        app/models/my_model.rb
        app/controllers/backend/my_models_controller.rb
        app/view/backend/my_models/_form.html.haml
        app/view/backend/my_models/index.html.haml
        app/view/backend/my_models/show.html.haml
        test/fixtures/my_models.yml
        test/models/my_model_test.rb
        test/controllers/backend/my_models_controller_test.rb
  
